Sentece: The results for 2.25% ivermectin: Cmax (37.11 ng/mL +/- 7.42), Tmax (16 days +/- 5.29), T(1/2) (44.62 days +/- 53.89), AUC (928.2 ng x day/mL +/- 153.83) and MRT (36.73 days +/- 33.64), and for 1.25% abamectin: Cmax (28.70 ng/mL +/- 9.54), Tmax (14 days +/- 4.04), T(1/2) (15.40 days +/- 11.43), AUC (618.05 ng x day/mL +/- 80.27) and MRT (20.79 days +/- 8.43) suggest that this combination of 2.25% ivermectin + 1.25% abamectin possesses properties that give this pharmaceutical formula a longer activity time than two of the commercial products tested (1% ivermectin and 1% abamectin), and showed similarity to 3.15% ivermectin.
